{"tid":1583371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日元朗點走？入嚟拆拆佢","createTime":"2019-09-20T14:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T15:56:25.000Z","uid":280525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d27bae8c10aa313218bfdbda10a4e600e1d595c","tid":1583371,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"921喺屯門落元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WYDHTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WYDHTp.jpg&h=3f3028d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，估下黨鐵會唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一開頭就封元朗打後既站</span></strong><br />\n巴士都一樣，（但上次天水圍無封輕鐵）<br />\n入嚟都難，但依加次次都難，<br />\n仲可以幾種方法配合加步行<br />\n<br />\n離開屯門<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MNdwLi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MNdwLi.jpg&h=bbccff4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1S0np5j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1S0np5j.jpg&h=12687de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQq7iG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQq7iG.jpg&h=6905594d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但問題嚟啦，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屯門去元朗</span></strong> 點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果無黨鐵巴士輕鐵 就得翻兩個選擇<br />\n一，揾方法出咗去，再入翻元朗<br />\n好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二，大隊一齊行到元朗<br />\n安全啲啲，帶啲唔識路既入<br />\n但依加班狗都大機會提早清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喺元朗走</span></strong><br />\n根據上次821，無封站，班狗喺各個出口推入嚟，<br />\n勇武手足幫手拉閘守住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他手足，和理非先可以搭到鐵走，<br />\n基本上無其他方法走，都怕喺其他出口有鄉黑<br />\n<br />\n今次，同樣狀況，仲要<strong>好大機會封站運狗</strong><br />\n咁就變咗狗可以係上下夾住我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢無封曬yoho出口，仲可以向雞地走，<br />\n但嗰邊都有鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該話邊邊出都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ztsw222.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtsw222.jpg&h=f52b49e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span></span></strong><br />\n會唔會話坐樓下輕鐵位，走都話係地面走，<br />\n可以穿過輕鐵出翻大馬路、雞地等等<br />\n行去朗屏，天水圍，洪水橋（雖然都難行）<br />\n唔似上面淨係可以穿商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又或者校巴會唔會可以一齊喺附近接<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大西北人表示覺得好難走，難過係港島入翻嚟<br />\n但嚟到就齊上齊落，仲有929 101<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊諗下點拆</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8ab1478d6b29c6ab602f5b2a8a1738ae0192b004","tid":1583371,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc0cc90eb82f3f7d6f29273ee6143ccf119f3bb","tid":1583371,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e891577fcf98e3d8ffcbfdebcccf0e086b40e280","tid":1583371,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53ad766129d7a4c9b1bbbf348db01fc64b1cbae","tid":1583371,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c501871ae48820df37252efcf5b07c184fde5d7","tid":158337